title: Player Attack S03E23 720p HDTV h264-Berg
description:
Bombshell might have originally been planned as a new Duke Nukem experience (before pesky lawsuits got in the way), but it's evolved into something even bigger and better, as Jonny Robot finds out.

We spend some time with Magic Duels: Origins, the latest Magic: The Gathering digital release, and explore just how it's different to earlier titles in the franchise.

Wondering what's good on the App Store? Jessica's been spending too much time on her phone again, and has three mobile games you should check out.
...plus, of course, we have all the latest gaming news as well - this is Player Attack!
